    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine runs roughly and produces noticeable noise, while the transmission exhibits signs of slipping during gear changes. Externally, the body shows several notable dents, rust spots, and fading paint. The interior also requires a deep clean and repair, with visible tears in the upholstery. This is a project car best suited for someone with mechanical expertise or for use as a parts vehicle.",
